@startuml
title Gson源码 策略模式+工厂方法模式

class "Gson" <<C>> {
    factories : List<TypeAdapterFactory>
}

interface TypeAdapterFactory {
    create(Gson gson, TypeToken<T> type) : <T> TypeAdapter<T>
}

interface TypeAdapter {
    read()
    write()
}

' Relationships from original diagram
TypeAdapter ..|> TypeAdapterFactory 
Gson *-- "1..*" TypeAdapterFactory 

note right of TypeAdapter::read(): Strategy Pattern\n(Concrete Strategies implement this)\nnote left of GSON*-->Factories: Factory Method Pattern\ntitle above note on top center:\n"Gson Source Code - \nStrategy + Factory Patterns"\n@enduml
